  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/98eac860b4937aabcfdcd6f1fd6ebea8.avif?t=1761095851\" width=602 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/0212a7501cef3f267bf649e3bd4dd39f.poster.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/0212a7501cef3f267bf649e3bd4dd39f.webm?t=1761095851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you speed up you live, if you slow down you die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must finish the 200km long road before the bomb explodes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When going fast, the bomb countdown stops. When you slow down, the countdown continues. And if time runs out, you'll blow up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you hit cars in traffic too fast, you'll explode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you hit some obstacles on the road too fast, you will explode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to be fast and careful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One small mistake could cost you your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your journey is long, with various obstacles, different seasons, day and night, and an adventure where you will feel the immersive speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can customize your car.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is similar to the only up game. You have to pass the 200 km long road by overcoming obstacles. If you hit cars in traffic 5 times quickly, you start over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/32ed0f9cd1639d62c56aef0811d2439a.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=191 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/62fd32bab6e74ee170d8179ba2f3b1a5.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=191 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/802949a4319aaf8e5b7ce21d41036e17.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=191 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/423127d8dfdc3cca9016161465965218.poster.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/423127d8dfdc3cca9016161465965218.webm?t=1761095851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/ceca3bb5ffa899f0f2aea61afe9955bf.poster.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/ceca3bb5ffa899f0f2aea61afe9955bf.webm?t=1761095851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/34587af9f9fe97dc8e4eca3d4df3826e.poster.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/34587af9f9fe97dc8e4eca3d4df3826e.webm?t=1761095851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/98eac860b4937aabcfdcd6f1fd6ebea8.avif?t=1761095851\" width=602 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/0212a7501cef3f267bf649e3bd4dd39f.poster.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/0212a7501cef3f267bf649e3bd4dd39f.webm?t=1761095851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you speed up you live, if you slow down you die.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You must finish the 200km long road before the bomb explodes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When going fast, the bomb countdown stops. When you slow down, the countdown continues. And if time runs out, you'll blow up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you hit cars in traffic too fast, you'll explode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you hit some obstacles on the road too fast, you will explode.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You have to be fast and careful.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One small mistake could cost you your life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your journey is long, with various obstacles, different seasons, day and night, and an adventure where you will feel the immersive speed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can customize your car.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is similar to the only up game. You have to pass the 200 km long road by overcoming obstacles. If you hit cars in traffic 5 times quickly, you start over.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/32ed0f9cd1639d62c56aef0811d2439a.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=191 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/62fd32bab6e74ee170d8179ba2f3b1a5.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=191 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/802949a4319aaf8e5b7ce21d41036e17.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=191 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/423127d8dfdc3cca9016161465965218.poster.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/423127d8dfdc3cca9016161465965218.webm?t=1761095851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/ceca3bb5ffa899f0f2aea61afe9955bf.poster.avif?t=1761095851\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1933160/extras/ceca3bb5ffa899f0f2aea61afe9955bf.webm?t=1761095851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_a